{"tid":285652,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"港產電影推介：《跛豪》（To Be Number One）","createTime":"2017-06-16T04:13:39.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-20T16:40:15.000Z","uid":7439,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"01e377ba6e1b65388ad179dac6dab60721270668","tid":285652,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T04:13:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/16/121154_8e1ee7cfb9620f4f310359b9c5adf1e6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F16%2F121154_8e1ee7cfb9620f4f310359b9c5adf1e6.jpg&h=ab4cb943&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/16/121155_741b002b0e4372b3c2529264222795fd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F16%2F121155_741b002b0e4372b3c2529264222795fd.jpg&h=4799c972&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/16/121156_5b05135439dd999f7b9df210a2078f75.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F16%2F121156_5b05135439dd999f7b9df210a2078f75.jpg&h=7b6883b1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/16/121157_21db3a90cc0b95e21c63f2de46211e42.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F16%2F121157_21db3a90cc0b95e21c63f2de46211e42.jpg&h=5dca7c15&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/16/121158_21db3a90cc0b95e21c63f2de46211e42.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F16%2F121158_21db3a90cc0b95e21c63f2de46211e42.jpg&h=854719bd&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/16/121217_e14fe86928b337d2689772a3688a0fd4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F16%2F121217_e14fe86928b337d2689772a3688a0fd4.jpg&h=d57aeea0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"http://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/06/16/121218_8a7876336631c54239355b54b23e409c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F06%2F16%2F121218_8a7876336631c54239355b54b23e409c.jpg&h=ddd37195&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n（電影部分截圖）<br />\n<br />\n《跛豪》（英文：To Be Number One）是一部於1991年上映的香港電影，由潘文傑擔任執導，以及由呂良偉、葉童等擔任領銜主演。<br />\n<br />\n此電影的主要內容以講述1960年代至1970年代的大毒梟&ldquo;跛豪&rdquo;（吳錫豪）的生平及事蹟作為人物事件背景題材，並定為「歷史傳記片」。<br />\n<br />\n此電影透過描述跛豪於1950年代末從中國大陸到香港，發蹟成為大毒梟，與貪污警察稱兄道弟，至1970年代由廉政公署成立後被捕，交織寫出當年香港的地下秩序和某層面的社會百態。<br />\n<br />\n此電影片長超過兩小時，在當時的港產片中屬少見的長篇電影。上映時票房超過3800萬，是當年的全年第三。<br />\n<br />\n香港電影金像獎（第11屆）<br />\n獎項\t名單\t結果<br />\n最佳電影\t跛豪\t獲獎<br />\n最佳導演\t潘文傑\t提名<br />\n最佳編劇\t麥當雄、蕭若元\t獲獎<br />\n最佳男主角\t呂良偉\t提名<br />\n最佳男配角\t鄭則仕\t提名<br />\n最佳女配角\t葉童\t提名<br />\n最佳剪接\t潘雄\t提名"},{"pid":"810f4c11fa5299961cc49bd238c6d75ba9dd211a","tid":285652,"uid":2757,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T04:40:23.000Z","msg":"雷洛傳好睇好多...<br />\n<br />\n陳惠敏, 秦煌同陸劍明都好好演技<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88f45d8c1f4f51f8439e431d096d446810fce629","tid":285652,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T04:44:13.000Z","msg":"D胡椒粉生意都撈到厭哂"},{"pid":"83185f4eabf2cd440514e842dad0a2c98268f015","tid":285652,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T04:47:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>D胡椒粉生意都撈到厭哂</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"332924940de1be3aa7add9b89a98f7cae402a8ab","tid":285652,"uid":42642,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T05:20:26.000Z","msg":"有親事都唔係香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n條仆街係先知黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"029d29126862a69b832ec00ee10694450e52e982","tid":285652,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T06:03:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有親事都唔係香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n條仆街係先知黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/38.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec8d7d78ac3b2e92e319bb27097324a04782477c","tid":285652,"uid":116896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T06:24:30.000Z","msg":"肥波好好戲<br />\n葉子媚食到雷老總又係奇招<br />\n仲搞到霞姐可以自立出套電影, 仲有返雷老總客串"},{"pid":"60115aeea278cc21aee81e8120c9d28d8ea4908a","tid":285652,"uid":103230,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T06:37:47.000Z","msg":"燒生好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34ab5847fb022bafe051d79c8c90a25bdc50eb90","tid":285652,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T06:53:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>肥波好好戲<br />\n葉子媚食到雷老總又係奇招<br />\n仲搞到霞姐可以自立出套電影, 仲有返雷老總客串</blockquote><br />\n超級公廁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e9beb9a00f3be745415a2d0ff39bb05434487b4","tid":285652,"uid":118057,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T06:55:48.000Z","msg":"果年呂良偉既跛豪輸左比獎門人，拎唔到影帝，真係可惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b8b380b29358b05fdc668674b1f21e4754b0a029","tid":285652,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T08:51:49.000Z","msg":"1969年，馬惜珍與其兄馬惜如一同創辦《東方日報》，由於馬氏兄弟與國民黨的關係良好，被視為親國民黨的「右派」，立場傾向中華民國政府及港英政府。<br />\n馬氏兄弟一直被視為有「跛豪」之稱的大毒梟吳錫豪之副手。1974年，吳錫豪終被警方毒品調查科拘捕，被判入獄30年，成為當時的香港司法史上最長的判刑。"},{"pid":"730a7bba5b1053e046942a21cffadad9dc8c990a","tid":285652,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T09:04:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1969年，馬惜珍與其兄馬惜如一同創辦《東方日報》，由於馬氏兄弟與國民黨的關係良好，被視為親國民黨的「右派」，立場傾向中華民國政府及港英政府。<br />\n馬氏兄弟一直被視為有「跛豪」之稱的大毒梟吳錫豪之副手。1974年，吳錫豪終被警方毒品調查科拘捕，被判入獄30年，成為當時的香港司法史上最長的判刑。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12ee5ae70a7d54c61ccd2119d7e3752ee5a08049","tid":285652,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T14:03:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>果年呂良偉既跛豪輸左比獎門人，拎唔到影帝，真係可惜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2bed04381de9cd2227c224f023eb3b8f2198de33","tid":285652,"uid":42820,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T14:16:57.000Z","msg":"燒山好野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f76e66b303c35fc3b15b4b12eef5923a44313ccf","tid":285652,"uid":3647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T14:20:30.000Z","msg":"成日係utube 睇"},{"pid":"94fd364f437ff3ff99e892e7be16ebf9e4a71eeb","tid":285652,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-16T17:16:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1969年，馬惜珍與其兄馬惜如一同創辦《東方日報》，由於馬氏兄弟與國民黨的關係良好，被視為親國民黨的「右派」，立場傾向中華民國政府及港英政府。<br />\n馬氏兄弟一直被視為有「跛豪」之稱的大毒梟吳錫豪之副手。1974年，吳錫豪終被警方毒品調查科拘捕，被判入獄30年，成為當時的香港司法史上最長的判刑。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5850027f1a9e381a915df2eb04881e044276ad19","tid":285652,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-17T04:01:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>1969年，馬惜珍與其兄馬惜如一同創辦《東方日報》，由於馬氏兄弟與國民黨的關係良好，被視為親國民黨的「右派」，立場傾向中華民國政府及港英政府。<br />\n馬氏兄弟一直被視為有「跛豪」之稱的大毒梟吳錫豪之副手。1974年，吳錫豪終被警方毒品調查科拘捕，被判入獄30年，成為當時的香港司法史上最長的判刑。</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n都唔知佢想講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"056f78f8a0d641e7a957ab4185c8445bc94f54fd","tid":285652,"uid":59898,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"repl